## DELIVERABLES / ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA
[ ] File uploads (resume, logo, avatar) work and store to cloud storage
[ ] OpenAI API calls work and are logged with token/cost tracking
[ ] Email notifications send for: signup, application, status change
[ ] Monthly AI cost cannot exceed configured budget (failsafe active)
[ ] .env.example is fully documented and pushed to repo
[ ] Total project cost breakdown is documented and reviewed
